      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Boston_1835-01_page02.jpg"/>
            <!--filenames for photos associated with this letter. Example: <pb n="1" facs="image1.jpg image2.jpg image3.jpg"/> -->
            <opener>
               <salute>
                  Private
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss Edgeworth</persName> begs to present<lb/>
               her compliments and thanks<lb/>
               to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#McGrJ1">Sir James M<hi rend = "superscript">c</hi>Grigor</persName><lb/>
               - She was much gratified<lb/>
               by his polite recollection of<lb/>
               her and if she might be <choice><orig>per-<lb/>
               mitted</orig><reg>permitted</reg></choice> to think that she<lb/>
               had any influence in <choice><orig>ob-<lb/>
                  taining</orig><reg>obtaining</reg></choice> in <persName ref="./Personography.xml#McGrJ1">James McGrigors</persName><lb/>
               attention to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#CoweX1">M<hi rend = "superscript">r.</hi> Cowen's</persName> <choice><orig>ap-<lb/>
               plication</orig><reg>application</reg></choice> for service she<lb/>
               must express her sense of the<lb/>
               obligation. - She has every<lb/>
               reason to believe that <persName ref="./Personography.xml#CoweX1">M<hi rend = "superscript">r.</hi><lb/>
               Cowen</persName> will do credit to his<lb/>
               
               <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Boston_1835-01_page03.jpg"/>
               education &amp; to his patron -<lb/> 
            </p>
            <closer>
               <address>
                  <!--Include any text written on the address leaf; use a separate "addrLine" for each line and indicate line breaks. -->
                  <addrLine><placeName>Edgeworthtown</placeName></addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Jan.<hi rend = "superscript">y</hi> 2<unclear>d</unclear> 1835</addrLine>
                  <addrLine/>
               </address>
            </closer>
         </div>
